OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPersistent
OL,6,Frain over Orkney turning heavy and
OL,7,Fextending to Shetland through the
OL,8,Fevening with snow on hills,
OL,9,FStrengthening winds with gales or
OL,10,Fsevere gales for a time tonight.
OL,11,FTurning drier over Orkney through the
OL,12,Fearly hours.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FAny remaining heavy rain, hill
OL,15,Fsnow and severe gales over Shetland
OL,16,Fclearing in the morning leaving a
OL,17,Fbright day with sunny intervals and a
OL,18,Ffew blustery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
